<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Moumou & Cie</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=Italiana&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
min-height: 100vh;
background: #f7f2eb;
font-family: ‘DM Sans’, sans-serif;
color: #2c1f16;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
padding: 60px 24px;
}

body::before {
content: “”;
position: fixed;
inset: 0;
background-image: url(“data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=‘0 0 512 512’ xmlns=‘http://www.w3.org/2000/svg’%3E%3Cfilter id=‘noise’%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=‘fractalNoise’ baseFrequency=‘0.65’ numOctaves=‘3’ stitchTiles=‘stitch’/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=‘100%25’ height=‘100%25’ filter=‘url(%23noise)’ opacity=‘0.03’/%3E%3C/svg%3E”);
pointer-events: none;
}

.wrapper {
width: 100%;
max-width: 380px;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
}

.avatar {
width: 90px; height: 90px;
border-radius: 50%;
object-fit: cover;
object-position: center top;
border: 3px solid white;
box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(160,82,45,0.18);
margin-bottom: 16px;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s forwards;
}

.name {
font-family: ‘Italiana’, serif;
font-size: 52px;
color: #2c1f16;
line-height: 0.95;
letter-spacing: -1px;
text-align: center;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s forwards;
}
.name em { font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif; font-style: italic; color: #a0522d; font-size: 56px; }

.tagline {
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 300;
color: #7a6658;
margin-top: 6px;
margin-bottom: 36px;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s forwards;
}

.links {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 12px;
width: 100%;
}

/* BASE BOUTON */
.btn {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 14px;
padding: 17px 22px;
border-radius: 18px;
text-decoration: none;
color: #2c1f16;
background: white;
border: 1px solid rgba(160,82,45,0.12);
box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(160,82,45,0.07);
transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
opacity: 0;
position: relative;
}
.btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(160,82,45,0.14); border-color: rgba(160,82,45,0.25); }

.btn-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.btn-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex: 1; }
.btn-label { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #2c1f16; }
.btn-sub { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: #a0522d; margin-top: 2px; }
.btn-name { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: #2c1f16; }
.btn-arrow { font-size: 18px; color: #a0522d; font-weight: 600; transition: transform 0.3s; }
.btn:hover .btn-arrow { transform: translateX(5px); }

/* SITE — mis en avant */
.btn-site {
background: white;
border: 2px solid #a0522d;
padding: 21px 22px;
box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(160,82,45,0.18);
animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.4s forwards;
}
.btn-site .btn-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #2c1f16; }
.btn-site .btn-arrow { color: #a0522d; font-size: 16px; }
.btn-site:hover { box-shadow: 0 16px 45px rgba(160,82,45,0.25); }

/* SIMULATEUR — mis en avant */
.btn-sim {
background: white;
border: 1.5px solid rgba(160,82,45,0.35);
box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(160,82,45,0.12);
animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.5s forwards;
overflow: visible;
}
.btn-sim::after {
content: “Gratuit ✨”;
position: absolute;
top: -10px; right: 14px;
background: #a0522d;
color: white;
font-size: 9px;
font-weight: 500;
letter-spacing: 1px;
text-transform: uppercase;
padding: 2px 10px;
border-radius: 20px;
}
.btn-sim .btn-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; }
.btn-sim:hover { box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(160,82,45,0.18); }

.btn-wa { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.6s forwards; }
.btn-ig { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.7s forwards; }
.btn-fb { animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.8s forwards; }

@keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);} }

footer {
margin-top: 36px;
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-style: italic;
font-size: 13px;
color: #c4a898;
opacity: 0;
animation: fadeUp 0.5s 1s forwards;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="wrapper">

  <img class="avatar" src="https://moumouandcie.github.io/IMG_4465.jpeg" alt="Lyna" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
  <h1 class="name">Moumou<br><em>& Cie</em></h1>
  <p class="tagline">Pet sitter professionnelle · Reims 🐾</p>

  <div class="links">

```
<a href="https://moumouandcie.github.io" target="_blank" class="btn btn-site">
  <span class="btn-icon">🌿</span>
  <div class="btn-content">
    <span class="btn-label">Mon site web</span>
    <span class="btn-sub">Découvrir Moumou & Cie →</span>
  </div>
</a>

<a href="https://moumouandcie.github.io/simulateur/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sim">
  <span class="btn-icon">💰</span>
  <div class="btn-content">
    <span class="btn-label">Simulateur de prix</span>
    <span class="btn-sub">Estimez le coût de votre garde →</span>
  </div>
</a>

<a href="https://wa.me/33619562866" target="_blank" class="btn btn-wa">
  <span class="btn-icon">💬</span>
  <span class="btn-name">WhatsApp</span>
  <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
</a>

<a href="https://instagram.com/moumou.and.cie" target="_blank" class="btn btn-ig">
  <span class="btn-icon">📸</span>
  <span class="btn-name">Instagram</span>
  <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
</a>

<a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=moumouandcie" target="_blank" class="btn btn-fb">
  <span class="btn-icon">📘</span>
  <span class="btn-name">Facebook</span>
  <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
</a>
```

  </div>

  <footer>Moumou & Cie — Reims</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
